<html><head><title>EQ2 Hot Zones Bonus Exp!</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>EQ2 Hot Zones Bonus Exp!</h3><p>This weekend SOE is <a href="http://eq2players.station.sony.com/news_archive_content.vm?id=3079&section=News&locale=en_US">giving up</a> bonus experience for play in certain "Hot Zones" from the original EverQuest 2. These bonus XP zones include The Caves, Commonlands, Sunken City, Nektulos Forest, Antonica, Enchanted Lands and Everfrost.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Friday, 8 May, 2009<br>Link: <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=52261">http://eqvault.ign.com/fullstory.php?id=52261</a><br>Printed On: Wed Sep 5 18:35:30 PDT 2012<br>©2008 IGN Entertainment</font></span>